  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a toaster or oven to toast rye bread slices until golden.",
    "While the bread toasts, melt butter in a small skillet over medium heat.",
    "Brush each toasted slice with the melted butter and set aside.",
    "In a bowl, whisk together sour cream, horseradish sauce, smoked paprika, salt, pepper, and chopped dill until silky smooth.",
    "Spread the creamy mixture evenly over each buttered toast slice.",
    "Top each slice with pineapple chunks and smoked salmon, arranging the salmon so the flesh faces up.",
    "Drizzle a small amount of lemon juice over the top and sprinkle lemon zest if using, then serve immediately."
  ],
